original_title: Richmond: Arthur Kill Road - Millvale Avenue
text:
211 Arthur Kill Road, north side, west of Millvale (Newvale) Avenue. This house was the home of S.H. Bailey (1917) and John Elliott (1907 and 1898). The dates refer to maps upon which the owners' names appear.

May 9, 1935

P. L. Sperr
